Regroupement de composants

Vous pouvez utiliser plusieurs mots-clés pour regrouper des composants et des interfaces

    package
    node
    folder
    frame
    cloud
    database

[Copy to clipboard]
[Edit online] 	

@startuml

package "Some Group" {
  HTTP - [First Component]
  [Another Component]
}

node "Other Groups" {
  FTP - [Second Component]
  [First Component] --> FTP
}

cloud {
  [Example 1]
}


database "MySql" {
  folder "This is my folder" {
    [Folder 3]
  }
  frame "Foo" {
    [Frame 4]
  }
}


[Another Component] --> [Example 1]
[Example 1] --> [Folder 3]
[Folder 3] --> [Frame 4]

@enduml

